query:
INSERT INTO watchlist (userId, movieId, movieTitle, moviePoster, movieType, movieRating, addedFrom)
SELECT 
  userId,
  movieId,
  movieTitle,
  moviePoster,
  movieType,
  movieRating,
  'swipe' as addedFrom
FROM saved_movies
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM watchlist 
  WHERE watchlist.userId = saved_movies.userId 
  AND watchlist.movieId = saved_movies.movieId
);
